title: some simplified types for it
pid: 27abd04b-b000-42de-8429-6440dd1067d9
body: |2-
  beside :: Traversal s t a b
         -> Traversal s' t' a b
         -> Traversal (s,s') (t,t') a b
  beside :: Lens s t a b
         -> Lens s' t' a b
         -> Traversal (s,s') (t,t') a b
  beside :: Fold s a
         -> Fold s' a
  -> Fold (s,s') a
